  - Title: Srimad Bhagavatam
    Location: XI xi
Tags:
  - Combat-Action=Pilgrimage-Descent Into Hell=The Descent Into Hell
---
To the man about to renounce the world the devas offer many
obstructions, hoping that his effort to transcend them and to attain
to Brahman will come to naught.
